# 📚 Plagiarism_Check-MERN – Plagiarism Checking Platform

![MERN](https://img.shields.io/badge/MERN-Stack-blueviolet?style=for-the-badge&logo=mongodb&logoColor=white)
![React](https://img.shields.io/badge/React-Vite-61DAFB?style=for-the-badge&logo=react&logoColor=black)
![Node.js](https://img.shields.io/badge/Node.js-Express-success?style=for-the-badge&logo=node.js&logoColor=white)
![API](https://img.shields.io/badge/Plagiarism-API-red?style=for-the-badge)


---

## 📖 Overview

**Plagiarism_Check-MERN** is a full-stack **MERN application** designed to **check plagiarism** in submitted text or documents. It interacts with the **plagiarismcheck.org API** to analyze content and provide detailed reports.

👉 This project is developed to provide a secure and intuitive platform for detecting plagiarism in educational or content creation scenarios.

---

## ✨ Features

### **👤 User Features (Frontend)**

* **📝 Text Submission:** Users can submit text or upload documents for plagiarism checks.
* **📊 Plagiarism Report:** Receive detailed reports with similarity scores and matched sources.
* **⏱️ Async Processing:** Status updates while the plagiarism check is in progress.

---

### **🛠️ Backend Features**

* **🔑 API Integration:** Securely communicates with the plagiarism checking API using an API token.
* **⏳ Status Polling:** Checks the progress of plagiarism analysis until completion.
* **📄 Report Fetching:** Retrieves final reports after plagiarism detection completes.

---

